      • getSharedGlobals

        IStorage getSharedGlobals()
        Returns the shared globals. These values are shared between all save slots.

        A common use for shared globals is to store global unlock data such as route clear flags.

      • getSaves

        java.util.Collection<ISaveFile> getSaves(int fromSlot,
                                         int numSlots)
        Fetches save file metadata for the save slots in the range [fromSlot, fromSlot+numSlots). For empty save slots, no information will be returned.
